channel.title: DubScape - PI
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/banner.png[/img]
[b]Hello im here today to release my most recent project, so i will begin with some info.[/b]
[b]Source:[/b] google
[b]Revision:[/b] 317 (PI)
[b]Client: [/b] Idfk, its PI im guessing? Its Full-screen however most of you have high resolution monitors so it probably just expanding/re-sizable.
[b]Other Info: [/b]Well Im not going to post any pictures because its pretty much the same old PI shit 600+ (yuck) The client support 300, 400, 500, and 600+ gameframe. The server itself is fairly stable, extremely more stable then other PI's. Garbage collector, and CycleEvents() have both been added to improved stability. This server is same old shit home is edgy however i was planning on making this a semi rs remake. So most if not all of lumby, varrock, fally, edgy, and barb village have been re-created. Also my Dungeoneering is in this. It needs some improvement its all in actionhandler, etc etc and what not. Never bothered to make a class for it. I only coded the first floor but its well coded and all known glitches were fixed. I never made a tele so the coords for the start are [b]3014, 5241[/b] give or take a few numbers. Everything's labelled and the dung consist of objectmanager.java, client.java, actionhandler.java, clickingbuttons.java, and dialoguehandler.java so feel free to rip it if you want to use it as a base please give credits. Has 100% gnome agil course no tele to it though, as well as all spell book go to correct spots with correct anim/gfx and require runes, and level and also give correct exp. (Includes teletabs) Gnome glider and ships are added boats need work. Server also has 100% firemaking just needs to be clipped! I have a 100% tutorial island but its not added if youd like it message me and ill give it to you. Theres no anti-leech so enjoy leeching.
[b]For media please look at my dev thread here:[/b]
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,518002.0.html
Ignore all the information before media as most of it is out-dated and incorrect. (including the website)
[b]Source: [/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?ih8ci2h0fianrru
[b]Client: [/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?1d152okfuuum3ec
[b][size=10pt]If your looking for a completed server then gtfo because this is nothing more then a base.[/size][/b]
[size=12pt][b]Bonus![/b][/size] If your looking to continue on with the name DUBSCAPE i have dubscape.no-ip.org and will transfer it to you, i also own the domain DUBSCAPE.ORG and will be open to offers/trade for it if you want it. With it will come the website its a runescape site remake so yeah. I also have the logo.
Im quiting to do real coding and follow my dream <3 Goodbye mopar.
Credits: Marcbob - 0% Really didnt do shit its same as other PI's but its base so whatever. Tyler - 30% Imsuperman05 - 20% Firemaking and other shit Me - 50%
People I'll Miss:
Imsuperman05 Tyb97 Riipiin SilentCj [B]FRIDDER!!![/B]
Some pics i made for shit just wanted to put on here...
[IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/banner.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/fm.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/dubscape.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/betasignup.jpg[/img]
Idk if ive missed anything if i did ill add it later..
goodbye.

item.dc:creator: @eballer48 eballer48
item.description:
@eballer48 wrote:

tyb97:

Why so many posts on this thread all of a sudden? Me and eric did this ages ago…

was… good times Anyways for those who asked, my dream is to write my own OS (operating system) At first I wanted to do this ya know? And I still do! However I’m a hardcore MS lover and i cant believe how incredible w7 is… I hate Apple with a passion and Linux is… just not me. Anyways back to my dream… I still want to write my own OS however as a personal project, I want to contribute and eventually work for microsoft <3 So I did some playing around with Java and wrote a few MineCraft bukkit plugins. After I felt I had a good knowledge of Java I moved on. I’m now playing TF2 and writing plugins for Sourcemod! Whos said you don’t learn anything from games? Fuck the system!
